    markdown:
      "## create\n\n`client.legacy.reporting.usageReports.voice.create(end_time: string, start_time: string, aggregation_type?: number, connections?: number[], managed_accounts?: string[], product_breakdown?: number, select_all_managed_accounts?: boolean): { data?: cdr_usage_report_response_legacy; }`\n\n**post** `/legacy/reporting/usage_reports/voice`\n\nCreates a new legacy usage V2 CDR report request with the specified filters\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `end_time: string`\n  End time in ISO format\n\n- `start_time: string`\n  Start time in ISO format\n\n- `aggregation_type?: number`\n  Aggregation type: All = 0, By Connections = 1, By Tags = 2, By Billing Group = 3\n\n- `connections?: number[]`\n  List of connections to filter by\n\n- `managed_accounts?: string[]`\n  List of managed accounts to include\n\n- `product_breakdown?: number`\n  Product breakdown type: No breakdown = 0, DID vs Toll-free = 1, Country = 2, DID vs Toll-free per Country = 3\n\n- `select_all_managed_accounts?: boolean`\n  Whether to select all managed accounts\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { id?: string; aggregation_type?: number; connections?: string[]; created_at?: string; end_time?: string; product_breakdown?: number; record_type?: string; report_url?: string; result?: object; start_time?: string; status?: number; updated_at?: string; }; }`\n\n  - `data?: { id?: string; aggregation_type?: number; connections?: string[]; created_at?: string; end_time?: string; product_breakdown?: number; record_type?: string; report_url?: string; result?: object; start_time?: string; status?: number; updated_at?: string; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst voice = await client.legacy.reporting.usageReports.voice.create({ end_time: '2024-02-01T00:00:00Z', start_time: '2024-02-01T00:00:00Z' });\n\nconsole.log(voice);\n```",
