    description:
      "Purchases and registers the specified amount of eSIMs to the current user's account.<br/><br/>\nIf <code>sim_card_group_id</code> is provided, the eSIMs will be associated with that group. Otherwise, the default group for the current user will be used.<br/><br/>\n",
