    markdown:
      "## validate\n\n`client.addresses.actions.validate(country_code: string, postal_code: string, street_address: string, administrative_area?: string, extended_address?: string, locality?: string): { data?: object; }`\n\n**post** `/addresses/actions/validate`\n\nValidates an address for emergency services.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `country_code: string`\n  The two-character (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2) country code of the address.\n\n- `postal_code: string`\n  The postal code of the address.\n\n- `street_address: string`\n  The primary street address information about the address.\n\n- `administrative_area?: string`\n  The locality of the address. For US addresses, this corresponds to the state of the address.\n\n- `extended_address?: string`\n  Additional street address information about the address such as, but not limited to, unit number or apartment number.\n\n- `locality?: string`\n  The locality of the address. For US addresses, this corresponds to the city of the address.\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { result: 'valid' | 'invalid'; suggested: { administrative_area?: string; country_code?: string; extended_address?: string; locality?: string; postal_code?: string; street_address?: string; }; errors?: object[]; record_type?: string; }; }`\n\n  - `data?: { result: 'valid' | 'invalid'; suggested: { administrative_area?: string; country_code?: string; extended_address?: string; locality?: string; postal_code?: string; street_address?: string; }; errors?: { code: string; title: string; description?: string; meta?: object; source?: { parameter?: string; pointer?: string; }; }[]; record_type?: string; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst response = await client.addresses.actions.validate({\n  country_code: 'US',\n  postal_code: '78701',\n  street_address: '600 Congress Avenue',\n});\n\nconsole.log(response);\n```",
