    markdown:
      "## delete\n\n`client.ai.assistants.delete(assistant_id: string): { id: string; deleted: boolean; object: string; }`\n\n**delete** `/ai/assistants/{assistant_id}`\n\nDelete an AI Assistant by `assistant_id`.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `assistant_id: string`\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ id: string; deleted: boolean; object: string; }`\n  Aligns with the OpenAI API:\nhttps://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/assistants/deleteAssistant\n\n  - `id: string`\n  - `deleted: boolean`\n  - `object: string`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst assistant = await client.ai.assistants.delete('assistant_id');\n\nconsole.log(assistant);\n```",
