      "## delete\n\n`client.ai.clusters.delete(task_id: string): void`\n\n**delete** `/ai/clusters/{task_id}`\n\nDelete a cluster\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `task_id: string`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nawait client.ai.clusters.delete('task_id')\n```",
