    qualified: 'client.ai.conversations.messages.list',
    params: ['conversation_id: string;'],
    response:
      "{ data: { role: 'user' | 'assistant' | 'tool'; text: string; created_at?: string; sent_at?: string; tool_calls?: { id: string; function: object; type: 'function'; }[]; }[]; meta: { page_number: number; page_size: number; total_pages: number; total_results: number; }; }",
    markdown:
      "## list\n\n`client.ai.conversations.messages.list(conversation_id: string): { data: object[]; meta: meta; }`\n\n**get** `/ai/conversations/{conversation_id}/messages`\n\nRetrieve messages for a specific conversation, including tool calls made by the assistant.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `conversation_id: string`\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data: { role: 'user' | 'assistant' | 'tool'; text: string; created_at?: string; sent_at?: string; tool_calls?: { id: string; function: object; type: 'function'; }[]; }[]; meta: { page_number: number; page_size: number; total_pages: number; total_results: number; }; }`\n\n  - `data: { role: 'user' | 'assistant' | 'tool'; text: string; created_at?: string; sent_at?: string; tool_calls?: { id: string; function: { arguments: string; name: string; }; type: 'function'; }[]; }[]`\n  - `meta: { page_number: number; page_size: number; total_pages: number; total_results: number; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst messages = await client.ai.conversations.messages.list('conversation_id');\n\nconsole.log(messages);\n```",
