    markdown:
      "## retrieve\n\n`client.chargesSummary.retrieve(end_date: string, start_date: string): { data: object; }`\n\n**get** `/charges_summary`\n\nRetrieve a summary of monthly charges for a specified date range. The date range cannot exceed 31 days.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `end_date: string`\n  End date for the charges summary in ISO date format (YYYY-MM-DD). The date is exclusive, data for the end_date itself is not included in the report. The interval between start_date and end_date cannot exceed 31 days.\n\n- `start_date: string`\n  Start date for the charges summary in ISO date format (YYYY-MM-DD)\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data: { currency: string; end_date: string; start_date: string; summary: { adjustments: object[]; lines: object | object[]; }; total: { credits: string; existing_mrc: string; grand_total: string; ledger_adjustments: string; new_mrc: string; new_otc: string; other: string; }; user_email: string; user_id: string; }; }`\n\n  - `data: { currency: string; end_date: string; start_date: string; summary: { adjustments: { amount: string; description: string; event_date: string; }[]; lines: { alias: string; existing_this_month: object; name: string; new_this_month: object; type: 'comparative'; } | { alias: string; amount: string; name: string; quantity: number; type: 'simple'; }[]; }; total: { credits: string; existing_mrc: string; grand_total: string; ledger_adjustments: string; new_mrc: string; new_otc: string; other: string; }; user_email: string; user_id: string; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst chargesSummary = await client.chargesSummary.retrieve({ end_date: '2025-06-01', start_date: '2025-05-01' });\n\nconsole.log(chargesSummary);\n```",
