    markdown:
      "## list_participants\n\n`client.conferences.listParticipants(conference_id: string, filter?: { muted?: boolean; on_hold?: boolean; whispering?: boolean; }, page[number]?: number, page[size]?: number, region?: 'Australia' | 'Europe' | 'Middle East' | 'US'): { id: string; call_control_id: string; call_leg_id: string; conference: object; created_at: string; end_conference_on_exit: boolean; muted: boolean; on_hold: boolean; record_type: 'participant'; soft_end_conference_on_exit: boolean; status: 'joining' | 'joined' | 'left'; updated_at: string; whisper_call_control_ids: string[]; }`\n\n**get** `/conferences/{conference_id}/participants`\n\nLists conference participants\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `conference_id: string`\n\n- `filter?: { muted?: boolean; on_hold?: boolean; whispering?: boolean; }`\n  Consolidated filter parameter (deepObject style). Originally: filter[muted], filter[on_hold], filter[whispering]\n  - `muted?: boolean`\n    If present, participants will be filtered to those who are/are not muted\n  - `on_hold?: boolean`\n    If present, participants will be filtered to those who are/are not put on hold\n  - `whispering?: boolean`\n    If present, participants will be filtered to those who are whispering or are not\n\n- `page[number]?: number`\n\n- `page[size]?: number`\n\n- `region?: 'Australia' | 'Europe' | 'Middle East' | 'US'`\n  Region where the conference data is located\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ id: string; call_control_id: string; call_leg_id: string; conference: { id?: string; name?: string; }; created_at: string; end_conference_on_exit: boolean; muted: boolean; on_hold: boolean; record_type: 'participant'; soft_end_conference_on_exit: boolean; status: 'joining' | 'joined' | 'left'; updated_at: string; whisper_call_control_ids: string[]; }`\n\n  - `id: string`\n  - `call_control_id: string`\n  - `call_leg_id: string`\n  - `conference: { id?: string; name?: string; }`\n  - `created_at: string`\n  - `end_conference_on_exit: boolean`\n  - `muted: boolean`\n  - `on_hold: boolean`\n  - `record_type: 'participant'`\n  - `soft_end_conference_on_exit: boolean`\n  - `status: 'joining' | 'joined' | 'left'`\n  - `updated_at: string`\n  - `whisper_call_control_ids: string[]`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\n// Automatically fetches more pages as needed.\nfor await (const conferenceListParticipantsResponse of client.conferences.listParticipants('conference_id')) {\n  console.log(conferenceListParticipantsResponse);\n}\n```",
