    markdown:
      "## end_conference\n\n`client.conferences.actions.endConference(id: string, command_id?: string): { data?: conference_command_result; }`\n\n**post** `/conferences/{id}/actions/end`\n\nEnd a conference and terminate all active participants.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `id: string`\n\n- `command_id?: string`\n  Use this field to avoid duplicate commands. Telnyx will ignore any command with the same `command_id` for the same conference.\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { result: string; }; }`\n\n  - `data?: { result: string; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst response = await client.conferences.actions.endConference('182bd5e5-6e1a-4fe4-a799-aa6d9a6ab26e');\n\nconsole.log(response);\n```",
