    markdown:
      "## update\n\n`client.externalConnections.update(id: string, outbound: { outbound_voice_profile_id: string; channel_limit?: number; }, active?: boolean, inbound?: { channel_limit?: number; }, tags?: string[], webhook_event_failover_url?: string, webhook_event_url?: string, webhook_timeout_secs?: number): { data?: external_connection; }`\n\n**patch** `/external_connections/{id}`\n\nUpdates settings of an existing External Connection based on the parameters of the request.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `id: string`\n\n- `outbound: { outbound_voice_profile_id: string; channel_limit?: number; }`\n  - `outbound_voice_profile_id: string`\n    Identifies the associated outbound voice profile.\n  - `channel_limit?: number`\n    When set, this will limit the number of concurrent outbound calls to phone numbers associated with this connection.\n\n- `active?: boolean`\n  Specifies whether the connection can be used.\n\n- `inbound?: { channel_limit?: number; }`\n  - `channel_limit?: number`\n    When set, this will limit the number of concurrent inbound calls to phone numbers associated with this connection.\n\n- `tags?: string[]`\n  Tags associated with the connection.\n\n- `webhook_event_failover_url?: string`\n  The failover URL where webhooks related to this connection will be sent if sending to the primary URL fails. Must include a scheme, such as 'https'.\n\n- `webhook_event_url?: string`\n  The URL where webhooks related to this connection will be sent. Must include a scheme, such as 'https'.\n\n- `webhook_timeout_secs?: number`\n  Specifies how many seconds to wait before timing out a webhook.\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { id?: string; active?: boolean; created_at?: string; credential_active?: boolean; external_sip_connection?: 'zoom' | 'operator_connect'; inbound?: object; outbound?: object; record_type?: string; tags?: string[]; updated_at?: string; webhook_api_version?: '1' | '2'; webhook_event_failover_url?: string; webhook_event_url?: string; webhook_timeout_secs?: number; }; }`\n\n  - `data?: { id?: string; active?: boolean; created_at?: string; credential_active?: boolean; external_sip_connection?: 'zoom' | 'operator_connect'; inbound?: { channel_limit?: number; }; outbound?: { channel_limit?: number; outbound_voice_profile_id?: string; }; record_type?: string; tags?: string[]; updated_at?: string; webhook_api_version?: '1' | '2'; webhook_event_failover_url?: string; webhook_event_url?: string; webhook_timeout_secs?: number; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst externalConnection = await client.externalConnections.update('1293384261075731499', { outbound: { outbound_voice_profile_id: '1911630617284445511' } });\n\nconsole.log(externalConnection);\n```",
