    params: ['agent_id: string;', 'body?: string;', 'phone_number?: string;'],
    response: '{ data: { url: string; }; }',
    markdown:
      "## generate_deeplink\n\n`client.messages.rcs.generateDeeplink(agent_id: string, body?: string, phone_number?: string): { data: object; }`\n\n**get** `/messages/rcs/deeplinks/{agent_id}`\n\nGenerate a deeplink URL that can be used to start an RCS conversation with a specific agent.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `agent_id: string`\n\n- `body?: string`\n  Pre-filled message body (URL encoded)\n\n- `phone_number?: string`\n  Phone number in E164 format (URL encoded)\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data: { url: string; }; }`\n\n  - `data: { url: string; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst response = await client.messages.rcs.generateDeeplink('agent_id');\n\nconsole.log(response);\n```",
