    markdown:
      "## invite_test_number\n\n`client.messaging.rcs.inviteTestNumber(id: string, phone_number: string): { data: object; }`\n\n**put** `/messaging/rcs/test_number_invite/{id}/{phone_number}`\n\nAdds a test phone number to an RCS agent for testing purposes.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `id: string`\n\n- `phone_number: string`\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data: { agent_id?: string; phone_number?: string; record_type?: 'rcs.test_number_invite'; status?: string; }; }`\n\n  - `data: { agent_id?: string; phone_number?: string; record_type?: 'rcs.test_number_invite'; status?: string; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst response = await client.messaging.rcs.inviteTestNumber('phone_number', { id: 'id' });\n\nconsole.log(response);\n```",
