      "## retrieve\n\n`client.messagingProfiles.retrieve(id: string): { data?: messaging_profile; }`\n\n**get** `/messaging_profiles/{id}`\n\nRetrieve a messaging profile\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `id: string`\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { id?: string; ai_assistant_id?: string; alpha_sender?: string; created_at?: string; daily_spend_limit?: string; daily_spend_limit_enabled?: boolean; enabled?: boolean; health_webhook_url?: string; mms_fall_back_to_sms?: boolean; mms_transcoding?: boolean; mobile_only?: boolean; name?: string; number_pool_settings?: number_pool_settings; organization_id?: string; record_type?: 'messaging_profile'; redaction_enabled?: boolean; redaction_level?: number; resource_group_id?: string; smart_encoding?: boolean; updated_at?: string; url_shortener_settings?: url_shortener_settings; v1_secret?: string; webhook_api_version?: '1' | '2' | '2010-04-01'; webhook_failover_url?: string; webhook_url?: string; whitelisted_destinations?: string[]; }; }`\n\n  - `data?: { id?: string; ai_assistant_id?: string; alpha_sender?: string; created_at?: string; daily_spend_limit?: string; daily_spend_limit_enabled?: boolean; enabled?: boolean; health_webhook_url?: string; mms_fall_back_to_sms?: boolean; mms_transcoding?: boolean; mobile_only?: boolean; name?: string; number_pool_settings?: { long_code_weight: number; skip_unhealthy: boolean; toll_free_weight: number; geomatch?: boolean; sticky_sender?: boolean; }; organization_id?: string; record_type?: 'messaging_profile'; redaction_enabled?: boolean; redaction_level?: number; resource_group_id?: string; smart_encoding?: boolean; updated_at?: string; url_shortener_settings?: { domain: string; prefix?: string; replace_blacklist_only?: boolean; send_webhooks?: boolean; }; v1_secret?: string; webhook_api_version?: '1' | '2' | '2010-04-01'; webhook_failover_url?: string; webhook_url?: string; whitelisted_destinations?: string[]; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst messagingProfile = await client.messagingProfiles.retrieve('182bd5e5-6e1a-4fe4-a799-aa6d9a6ab26e');\n\nconsole.log(messagingProfile);\n```",
