    markdown:
      "## retrieve\n\n`client.otaUpdates.retrieve(id: string): { data?: object; }`\n\n**get** `/ota_updates/{id}`\n\nThis API returns the details of an Over the Air (OTA) update.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `id: string`\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { id?: string; created_at?: string; record_type?: string; settings?: { mobile_network_operators_preferences?: object[]; }; sim_card_id?: string; status?: 'in-progress' | 'completed' | 'failed'; type?: 'sim_card_network_preferences'; updated_at?: string; }; }`\n\n  - `data?: { id?: string; created_at?: string; record_type?: string; settings?: { mobile_network_operators_preferences?: { mobile_network_operator_id?: string; mobile_network_operator_name?: string; priority?: number; }[]; }; sim_card_id?: string; status?: 'in-progress' | 'completed' | 'failed'; type?: 'sim_card_network_preferences'; updated_at?: string; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst otaUpdate = await client.otaUpdates.retrieve('6a09cdc3-8948-47f0-aa62-74ac943d6c58');\n\nconsole.log(otaUpdate);\n```",
