      "## change_bundle_status\n\n`client.phoneNumbers.actions.changeBundleStatus(id: string, bundle_id: string): { data?: phone_number_with_voice_settings; }`\n\n**patch** `/phone_numbers/{id}/actions/bundle_status_change`\n\nChange the bundle status for a phone number (set to being in a bundle or remove from a bundle)\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `id: string`\n\n- `bundle_id: string`\n  The new bundle_id setting for the number. If you are assigning the number to a bundle, this is the unique ID of the bundle you wish to use. If you are removing the number from a bundle, this must be null. You cannot assign a number from one bundle to another directly. You must first remove it from a bundle, and then assign it to a new bundle.\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { id?: string; call_forwarding?: call_forwarding; call_recording?: call_recording; cnam_listing?: cnam_listing; connection_id?: string; customer_reference?: string; emergency?: object; inbound_call_screening?: 'disabled' | 'reject_calls' | 'flag_calls'; media_features?: media_features; phone_number?: string; record_type?: string; tech_prefix_enabled?: boolean; translated_number?: string; usage_payment_method?: 'pay-per-minute' | 'channel'; }; }`\n\n  - `data?: { id?: string; call_forwarding?: { call_forwarding_enabled?: boolean; forwarding_type?: 'always' | 'on-failure'; forwards_to?: string; }; call_recording?: { inbound_call_recording_channels?: 'single' | 'dual'; inbound_call_recording_enabled?: boolean; inbound_call_recording_format?: 'wav' | 'mp3'; }; cnam_listing?: { cnam_listing_details?: string; cnam_listing_enabled?: boolean; }; connection_id?: string; customer_reference?: string; emergency?: { emergency_address_id?: string; emergency_enabled?: boolean; emergency_status?: 'disabled' | 'active' | 'provisioning' | 'deprovisioning' | 'provisioning-failed'; }; inbound_call_screening?: 'disabled' | 'reject_calls' | 'flag_calls'; media_features?: { accept_any_rtp_packets_enabled?: boolean; rtp_auto_adjust_enabled?: boolean; t38_fax_gateway_enabled?: boolean; }; phone_number?: string; record_type?: string; tech_prefix_enabled?: boolean; translated_number?: string; usage_payment_method?: 'pay-per-minute' | 'channel'; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst response = await client.phoneNumbers.actions.changeBundleStatus('1293384261075731499', { bundle_id: '5194d8fc-87e6-4188-baa9-1c434bbe861b' });\n\nconsole.log(response);\n```",
