    response: '{ data?: { activation_code?: string; record_type?: string; }; }',
    markdown:
      "## get_activation_code\n\n`client.simCards.getActivationCode(id: string): { data?: object; }`\n\n**get** `/sim_cards/{id}/activation_code`\n\nIt returns the activation code for an eSIM.<br/><br/>\n This API is only available for eSIMs. If the given SIM is a physical SIM card, or has already been installed, an error will be returned.\n\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `id: string`\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { activation_code?: string; record_type?: string; }; }`\n\n  - `data?: { activation_code?: string; record_type?: string; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst response = await client.simCards.getActivationCode('6a09cdc3-8948-47f0-aa62-74ac943d6c58');\n\nconsole.log(response);\n```",
