      '{ data?: { categories?: { bytes_received?: number; bytes_sent?: number; category?: string; ops?: number; successful_ops?: number; }[]; timestamp?: string; total?: { bytes_received?: number; bytes_sent?: number; ops?: number; successful_ops?: number; }; }[]; }',
    markdown:
      "## get_api_usage\n\n`client.storage.buckets.usage.getAPIUsage(bucketName: string, filter: { end_time: string; start_time: string; }): { data?: object[]; }`\n\n**get** `/storage/buckets/{bucketName}/usage/api`\n\nReturns the detail on API usage on a bucket of a particular time period, group by method category.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `bucketName: string`\n\n- `filter: { end_time: string; start_time: string; }`\n  Consolidated filter parameter (deepObject style). Originally: filter[start_time], filter[end_time]\n  - `end_time: string`\n    The end time of the period to filter the usage (ISO microsecond format)\n  - `start_time: string`\n    The start time of the period to filter the usage (ISO microsecond format)\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { categories?: { bytes_received?: number; bytes_sent?: number; category?: string; ops?: number; successful_ops?: number; }[]; timestamp?: string; total?: { bytes_received?: number; bytes_sent?: number; ops?: number; successful_ops?: number; }; }[]; }`\n\n  - `data?: { categories?: { bytes_received?: number; bytes_sent?: number; category?: string; ops?: number; successful_ops?: number; }[]; timestamp?: string; total?: { bytes_received?: number; bytes_sent?: number; ops?: number; successful_ops?: number; }; }[]`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst response = await client.storage.buckets.usage.getAPIUsage('', { filter: { end_time: '2019-12-27T18:11:19.117Z', start_time: '2019-12-27T18:11:19.117Z' } });\n\nconsole.log(response);\n```",
