    markdown:
      "## retrieve_transcriptions_json\n\n`client.texml.accounts.retrieveTranscriptionsJson(account_sid: string, PageSize?: number, PageToken?: string): { end?: number; first_page_uri?: string; next_page_uri?: string; page?: number; page_size?: number; previous_page_uri?: string; start?: number; transcriptions?: object[]; uri?: string; }`\n\n**get** `/texml/Accounts/{account_sid}/Transcriptions.json`\n\nReturns multiple recording transcription resources for an account.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `account_sid: string`\n\n- `PageSize?: number`\n  The number of records to be displayed on a page\n\n- `PageToken?: string`\n  Used to request the next page of results.\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ end?: number; first_page_uri?: string; next_page_uri?: string; page?: number; page_size?: number; previous_page_uri?: string; start?: number; transcriptions?: { account_sid?: string; api_version?: string; call_sid?: string; date_created?: string; date_updated?: string; duration?: string; recording_sid?: string; sid?: string; status?: 'in-progress' | 'completed'; transcription_text?: string; uri?: string; }[]; uri?: string; }`\n\n  - `end?: number`\n  - `first_page_uri?: string`\n  - `next_page_uri?: string`\n  - `page?: number`\n  - `page_size?: number`\n  - `previous_page_uri?: string`\n  - `start?: number`\n  - `transcriptions?: { account_sid?: string; api_version?: string; call_sid?: string; date_created?: string; date_updated?: string; duration?: string; recording_sid?: string; sid?: string; status?: 'in-progress' | 'completed'; transcription_text?: string; uri?: string; }[]`\n  - `uri?: string`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst response = await client.texml.accounts.retrieveTranscriptionsJson('account_sid');\n\nconsole.log(response);\n```",
