    markdown:
      "## retrieve\n\n`client.texml.accounts.calls.retrieve(account_sid: string, call_sid: string): { account_sid?: string; answered_by?: 'human' | 'machine' | 'not_sure'; caller_name?: string; date_created?: string; date_updated?: string; direction?: 'inbound' | 'outbound'; duration?: string; end_time?: string; from?: string; from_formatted?: string; price?: string; price_unit?: string; sid?: string; start_time?: string; status?: 'ringing' | 'in-progress' | 'canceled' | 'completed' | 'failed' | 'busy' | 'no-answer'; to?: string; to_formatted?: string; uri?: string; }`\n\n**get** `/texml/Accounts/{account_sid}/Calls/{call_sid}`\n\nReturns an individual call identified by its CallSid. This endpoint is eventually consistent.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `account_sid: string`\n\n- `call_sid: string`\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ account_sid?: string; answered_by?: 'human' | 'machine' | 'not_sure'; caller_name?: string; date_created?: string; date_updated?: string; direction?: 'inbound' | 'outbound'; duration?: string; end_time?: string; from?: string; from_formatted?: string; price?: string; price_unit?: string; sid?: string; start_time?: string; status?: 'ringing' | 'in-progress' | 'canceled' | 'completed' | 'failed' | 'busy' | 'no-answer'; to?: string; to_formatted?: string; uri?: string; }`\n\n  - `account_sid?: string`\n  - `answered_by?: 'human' | 'machine' | 'not_sure'`\n  - `caller_name?: string`\n  - `date_created?: string`\n  - `date_updated?: string`\n  - `direction?: 'inbound' | 'outbound'`\n  - `duration?: string`\n  - `end_time?: string`\n  - `from?: string`\n  - `from_formatted?: string`\n  - `price?: string`\n  - `price_unit?: string`\n  - `sid?: string`\n  - `start_time?: string`\n  - `status?: 'ringing' | 'in-progress' | 'canceled' | 'completed' | 'failed' | 'busy' | 'no-answer'`\n  - `to?: string`\n  - `to_formatted?: string`\n  - `uri?: string`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst call = await client.texml.accounts.calls.retrieve('call_sid', { account_sid: 'account_sid' });\n\nconsole.log(call);\n```",
