    markdown:
      "## delete_recording_sid_json\n\n`client.texml.accounts.recordings.json.deleteRecordingSidJson(account_sid: string, recording_sid: string): void`\n\n**delete** `/texml/Accounts/{account_sid}/Recordings/{recording_sid}.json`\n\nDeletes recording resource identified by recording id.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `account_sid: string`\n\n- `recording_sid: string`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nawait client.texml.accounts.recordings.json.deleteRecordingSidJson('6a09cdc3-8948-47f0-aa62-74ac943d6c58', { account_sid: 'account_sid' })\n```",
