      "## retrieve_recording_sid_json\n\n`client.texml.accounts.recordings.json.retrieveRecordingSidJson(account_sid: string, recording_sid: string): { account_sid?: string; call_sid?: string; channels?: 1 | 2; conference_sid?: string; date_created?: string; date_updated?: string; duration?: string; error_code?: string; media_url?: string; sid?: string; source?: string; start_time?: string; status?: 'in-progress' | 'completed' | 'paused' | 'stopped'; subresources_uris?: texml_recording_subresources_uris; uri?: string; }`\n\n**get** `/texml/Accounts/{account_sid}/Recordings/{recording_sid}.json`\n\nReturns recording resource identified by recording id.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `account_sid: string`\n\n- `recording_sid: string`\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ account_sid?: string; call_sid?: string; channels?: 1 | 2; conference_sid?: string; date_created?: string; date_updated?: string; duration?: string; error_code?: string; media_url?: string; sid?: string; source?: string; start_time?: string; status?: 'in-progress' | 'completed' | 'paused' | 'stopped'; subresources_uris?: { transcriptions?: string; }; uri?: string; }`\n\n  - `account_sid?: string`\n  - `call_sid?: string`\n  - `channels?: 1 | 2`\n  - `conference_sid?: string`\n  - `date_created?: string`\n  - `date_updated?: string`\n  - `duration?: string`\n  - `error_code?: string`\n  - `media_url?: string`\n  - `sid?: string`\n  - `source?: string`\n  - `start_time?: string`\n  - `status?: 'in-progress' | 'completed' | 'paused' | 'stopped'`\n  - `subresources_uris?: { transcriptions?: string; }`\n  - `uri?: string`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst texmlGetCallRecordingResponseBody = await client.texml.accounts.recordings.json.retrieveRecordingSidJson('6a09cdc3-8948-47f0-aa62-74ac943d6c58', { account_sid: 'account_sid' });\n\nconsole.log(texmlGetCallRecordingResponseBody);\n```",
