      "## trigger_whatsapp_verification\n\n`client.verifications.triggerWhatsappVerification(phone_number: string, verify_profile_id: string, custom_code?: string, timeout_secs?: number): { data: verification; }`\n\n**post** `/verifications/whatsapp`\n\nTrigger WhatsApp verification\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `phone_number: string`\n  +E164 formatted phone number.\n\n- `verify_profile_id: string`\n  The identifier of the associated Verify profile.\n\n- `custom_code?: string`\n  Send a self-generated numeric code to the end-user\n\n- `timeout_secs?: number`\n  The number of seconds the verification code is valid for.\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data: { id?: string; created_at?: string; custom_code?: string; phone_number?: string; record_type?: 'verification'; status?: 'pending' | 'accepted' | 'invalid' | 'expired' | 'error'; timeout_secs?: number; type?: 'sms' | 'call' | 'flashcall' | 'whatsapp'; updated_at?: string; verify_profile_id?: string; }; }`\n\n  - `data: { id?: string; created_at?: string; custom_code?: string; phone_number?: string; record_type?: 'verification'; status?: 'pending' | 'accepted' | 'invalid' | 'expired' | 'error'; timeout_secs?: number; type?: 'sms' | 'call' | 'flashcall' | 'whatsapp'; updated_at?: string; verify_profile_id?: string; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst createVerificationResponse = await client.verifications.triggerWhatsappVerification({ phone_number: '+13035551234', verify_profile_id: '12ade33a-21c0-473b-b055-b3c836e1c292' });\n\nconsole.log(createVerificationResponse);\n```",
