    markdown:
      "## retrieve\n\n`client.virtualCrossConnects.retrieve(id: string): { data?: record & network_interface; }`\n\n**get** `/virtual_cross_connects/{id}`\n\nRetrieve a Virtual Cross Connect.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `id: string`\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { id?: string; created_at?: string; record_type?: string; updated_at?: string; } & { name?: string; network_id?: string; status?: interface_status; }; }`\n\n  - `data?: { id?: string; created_at?: string; record_type?: string; updated_at?: string; } & { name?: string; network_id?: string; status?: 'created' | 'provisioning' | 'provisioned' | 'deleting'; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst virtualCrossConnect = await client.virtualCrossConnects.retrieve('6a09cdc3-8948-47f0-aa62-74ac943d6c58');\n\nconsole.log(virtualCrossConnect);\n```",
