    response:
      "{ data?: { id?: string; category?: 'MARKETING' | 'UTILITY' | 'AUTHENTICATION'; components?: object[]; created_at?: string; language?: string; name?: string; record_type?: string; rejection_reason?: string; status?: string; template_id?: string; updated_at?: string; whatsapp_business_account?: object; }; }",
    markdown:
      "## create\n\n`client.whatsapp.templates.create(category: 'MARKETING' | 'UTILITY' | 'AUTHENTICATION', components: { format: 'TEXT' | 'IMAGE' | 'VIDEO' | 'DOCUMENT' | 'LOCATION'; type: 'HEADER'; example?: { header_handle?: string[]; header_text?: string[]; }; text?: string; } | { type: 'BODY'; example?: { body_text?: string[][]; }; text?: string; } | { type: 'FOOTER'; code_expiration_minutes?: number; text?: string; } | { buttons: { type: 'URL' | 'PHONE_NUMBER' | 'QUICK_REPLY' | 'OTP' | 'COPY_CODE' | 'FLOW'; autofill_text?: string; example?: string[]; flow_action?: 'navigate' | 'data_exchange'; flow_id?: string; navigate_screen?: string; otp_type?: 'COPY_CODE' | 'ONE_TAP'; package_name?: string; phone_number?: string; signature_hash?: string; text?: string; url?: string; zero_tap_terms_accepted?: boolean; }[]; type: 'BUTTONS'; } | { cards: { components?: object[]; }[]; type: 'CAROUSEL'; }[], language: string, name: string, waba_id: string): { data?: whatsapp_template_data; }`\n\n**post** `/v2/whatsapp/message_templates`\n\nCreate a Whatsapp message template\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `category: 'MARKETING' | 'UTILITY' | 'AUTHENTICATION'`\n  Template category: AUTHENTICATION, UTILITY, or MARKETING.\n\n- `components: { format: 'TEXT' | 'IMAGE' | 'VIDEO' | 'DOCUMENT' | 'LOCATION'; type: 'HEADER'; example?: { header_handle?: string[]; header_text?: string[]; }; text?: string; } | { type: 'BODY'; example?: { body_text?: string[][]; }; text?: string; } | { type: 'FOOTER'; code_expiration_minutes?: number; text?: string; } | { buttons: { type: 'URL' | 'PHONE_NUMBER' | 'QUICK_REPLY' | 'OTP' | 'COPY_CODE' | 'FLOW'; autofill_text?: string; example?: string[]; flow_action?: 'navigate' | 'data_exchange'; flow_id?: string; navigate_screen?: string; otp_type?: 'COPY_CODE' | 'ONE_TAP'; package_name?: string; phone_number?: string; signature_hash?: string; text?: string; url?: string; zero_tap_terms_accepted?: boolean; }[]; type: 'BUTTONS'; } | { cards: { components?: object[]; }[]; type: 'CAROUSEL'; }[]`\n  Template components defining message structure. Passed through to Meta Graph API. Templates with variables must include example values. Supports HEADER, BODY, FOOTER, BUTTONS, CAROUSEL and any future Meta component types.\n\n- `language: string`\n  Template language code (e.g. en_US, es, pt_BR).\n\n- `name: string`\n  Template name. Lowercase letters, numbers, and underscores only.\n\n- `waba_id: string`\n  The WhatsApp Business Account ID.\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data?: { id?: string; category?: 'MARKETING' | 'UTILITY' | 'AUTHENTICATION'; components?: object[]; created_at?: string; language?: string; name?: string; record_type?: string; rejection_reason?: string; status?: string; template_id?: string; updated_at?: string; whatsapp_business_account?: object; }; }`\n\n  - `data?: { id?: string; category?: 'MARKETING' | 'UTILITY' | 'AUTHENTICATION'; components?: object[]; created_at?: string; language?: string; name?: string; record_type?: string; rejection_reason?: string; status?: string; template_id?: string; updated_at?: string; whatsapp_business_account?: { id?: string; }; }`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst template = await client.whatsapp.templates.create({\n  category: 'MARKETING',\n  components: [{ format: 'TEXT', type: 'HEADER' }],\n  language: 'language',\n  name: 'name',\n  waba_id: 'waba_id',\n});\n\nconsole.log(template);\n```",
