    markdown:
      "## list\n\n`client.voiceClones.list(filter[name]?: string, filter[provider]?: 'telnyx' | 'minimax', page[number]?: number, page[size]?: number, sort?: 'name' | '-name' | 'created_at' | '-created_at'): { id?: string; created_at?: string; gender?: 'male' | 'female' | 'neutral'; label?: string; language?: string; name?: string; provider?: 'telnyx' | 'minimax'; provider_supported_models?: string[]; provider_voice_id?: string; record_type?: 'voice_clone'; source_voice_design_id?: string; source_voice_design_version?: number; updated_at?: string; }`\n\n**get** `/voice_clones`\n\nReturns a paginated list of voice clones belonging to the authenticated account.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `filter[name]?: string`\n  Case-insensitive substring filter on the name field.\n\n- `filter[provider]?: 'telnyx' | 'minimax'`\n  Filter by voice synthesis provider. Case-insensitive.\n\n- `page[number]?: number`\n  Page number for pagination (1-based).\n\n- `page[size]?: number`\n  Number of results per page.\n\n- `sort?: 'name' | '-name' | 'created_at' | '-created_at'`\n  Sort order. Prefix with `-` for descending. Defaults to `-created_at`.\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ id?: string; created_at?: string; gender?: 'male' | 'female' | 'neutral'; label?: string; language?: string; name?: string; provider?: 'telnyx' | 'minimax'; provider_supported_models?: string[]; provider_voice_id?: string; record_type?: 'voice_clone'; source_voice_design_id?: string; source_voice_design_version?: number; updated_at?: string; }`\n  A voice clone object.\n\n  - `id?: string`\n  - `created_at?: string`\n  - `gender?: 'male' | 'female' | 'neutral'`\n  - `label?: string`\n  - `language?: string`\n  - `name?: string`\n  - `provider?: 'telnyx' | 'minimax'`\n  - `provider_supported_models?: string[]`\n  - `provider_voice_id?: string`\n  - `record_type?: 'voice_clone'`\n  - `source_voice_design_id?: string`\n  - `source_voice_design_version?: number`\n  - `updated_at?: string`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\n// Automatically fetches more pages as needed.\nfor await (const voiceCloneData of client.voiceClones.list()) {\n  console.log(voiceCloneData);\n}\n```",
