    stainlessPath: '(resource) voice_clones > (method) download_sample',
    qualified: 'client.voiceClones.downloadSample',
    params: ['id: string;'],
    response: 'string',
    markdown:
      "## download_sample\n\n`client.voiceClones.downloadSample(id: string): string`\n\n**get** `/voice_clones/{id}/sample`\n\nDownloads the WAV audio sample that was used to create the voice clone.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `id: string`\n\n### Returns\n\n- `string`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Telnyx from 'telnyx';\n\nconst client = new Telnyx();\n\nconst response = await client.voiceClones.downloadSample('182bd5e5-6e1a-4fe4-a799-aa6d9a6ab26e');\n\nconsole.log(response);\n\nconst content = await response.blob()\nconsole.log(content)\n```",
